nt to receive location updates while running in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"background, you must use the Core Location framework."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true},{"text":" object from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"text":" property of the map view displayed in your application.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","type":"topic","title":"MLNUserLocation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:didUpdateUserLocation:":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:didUpdateUserLocation:","title":"mapView:didUpdateUserLocation:","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:didupdateuserlocation:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:didUpdateUserLocation:"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Tells the delegate that the location of the user was updated.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":